<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Result</title>
</head>
<style>

    span {
        color: blue;
        font-weight: 700;
    }
</style>
<body>

        <h1><%= title %></h1>

        <div>
            <span><%= formData.name %></span>님 환영합니다.
        </div>

        <div>
            성별은
            <span> <%= formData.gender === 'man' && '남자' || formData.gender === 'woman' && '여자' %> </span>
            이군요!
        </div>
    
        <div>
            <span> <%= formData.birth %> </span> 에 태어나셨군요!
        </div>

        <div>
            관심사가 <%= formData.interest === '' ? '관심사가 없으시군요!' : '' %> 
            <span><%= formData.interest != '' ? formData.interest + '이군요!' : '' %> </p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
            좋아하는 컬러는
            <div style="width: 10px; height: 10px; display: inline-block;" id="fvColor"></div> 
            이군요!
        </div>
        <div>
            좋아하는 숫자는 <%= formData.fvNumber === '' ? '없으시군요!' : '' %> 
            <span><%= formData.fvNumber != '' ? formData.fvNumber + '이군요!' : '' %> </p>
        </div>

        <br/>
        <a href="/">홈으로 이동</a>

        <script>
            document.getElementById('fvColor').style.backgroundColor  = '<%= formData.fvColor %>';
        </script>
</body>
</html>